-2701","markText":"第一个，我们利用排除说明了心理抑制理论比以前更值得怀疑，因为我们的实验结果已经对它做出了否定。所有借助经验或活动来表达价值的教育理论，由于没有考虑到方向和结果而让人不能接受。第二点，在我们的生活和学习中，一种情境将引起一种特定的反应，但如果仅仅是简单的情境重复，那它的作用将是非常小的，几乎不可能成为有利或有害的主重因素。","totalCount":14,"users":[{"userVid":7400582,"name":"奥奥","nick":"奥奥","gender":1,"avatar":"https://res.weread.qq.com/wravatar/WV0005-KqySzSFILl5BhITZaX0iq97/0"},{"userVid":238955592,"name":"smiling","gender":2,"avatar":"https://wx.qlogo.cn/mmhead/PiajxSqBRaEKQe55pCcbO91RFdD9rnK1UWjXdofjmcHKkW6BSs7uhhg/0"},{"userVid":11416567,"name":"文成公与文正公的小徒弟叫小宋","nick":"文成公与文正公的小徒弟叫小宋","gender":1,"avatar":"https://wx.qlogo.cn/mmhead/Q3auHgzwzM4fPOOZADfU2RM7SpjY8Mbh3eYuKicA43tHmVict21ia3wGw/0"}]},{"bookId":"931773","userVid":15900475,"bookmarkId":"931773_10_9724-9785","chapterUid":10,"range":"9724-9785","markText":"尽管它们的重复次数很少，但是只要从属关系越强，就能得到更强的联结强度。所以说，序列并不能导致更强的联结，而从属关系却可以。","totalCount":14,"users":[{"userVid":219953890,"name":"兆亿间","gender":1,"avatar":"https://thirdwx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/vi_32/91ibs2dfLBMZo1Hnsab23iatyUeTtClJQKW8SKibib07YtPrJpS4OCu7Okvtvxl7WIRLsiauNbvVP5F9DeCzsRicLH0A/132"},{"userVid":15900475,"name":"朱淦","gender":1,"avatar":"https://thirdwx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/vi_32/3u8icNZ0rd4EvJVEqW6aBPkWlPSbiaxKONHOopqib8icYn1ww1iaXUjUetpmJfdyfjq4tZTSW7Ots1Y9drS6vhgZNibg/132","isV":0,"vDesc":"凡事预则立 不预则废"},{"userVid":265386725,"name":"ししざ","gender":0,"avatar":"http://thirdwx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/vi_32/2tA1EskBGs4hMZ9hJpj8LdktiaAupqdLLYbK7DPQRw6nqSVRoqOROlGibSG6UrMbcLarCIW3wa3bb2AKBG0Y1v2A/132"}]},{"bookId":"931773","userVid":230117358,"bookmarkId":"931773_5_3207-3232","chapterUid":5,"range":"3207-3232","markText":"学习就是习得新的反应并改变其对生活情境的联结强度。","totalCount":12,"users":[{"userVid":54702459,"name":"落日长河","gender":1,"avatar":"https://thirdwx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/vi_32/DYAIOgq83epqzXxKHrGxfBDVZhInhUuQMXeibP5Svic3JbyJtREmpjU4nhPOaNFEtnfeEY0UkCKyYHoPg1DicYiagA/132"},{"userVid":12407977,"name":"J","gender":1,"avatar":"https://thirdwx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/vi_32/ica2sO8ico1AuiaRUzo4okwJMXDOIYX4qZcTAm1VVFHiaotp0DHCTzKHtqVdfelSBOk1XRib